336
00:26:25,753 --> 00:26:31,424
不過米格28的反向飛行油箱確有問題
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}However, the MiG-28 does have a problem with its inverted flight tanks.{\r}

337
00:26:31,626 --> 00:26:34,595
它不擅長做負重力飛行動作
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}It won't do a negative-G pushover.{\r}

338
00:26:34,796 --> 00:26:37,822
最新的情報告訴我們它最多
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}The latest intelligence tells us that the most it will do{\r}

