340
00:26:40,635 --> 00:26:42,694
對不起，上尉
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Excuse me, lieutenant.{\r}

341
00:26:42,904 --> 00:26:44,428
有什麼問題嗎？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Is there something wrong?{\r}

342
00:26:44,639 --> 00:26:47,107
女士，米格戰機的資料不正確
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Yes, ma'am, the data on the MiG is inaccurate.{\r}

343
00:26:48,810 --> 00:26:50,869
