345
00:26:54,242 --> 00:26:55,436
對不起，笨鵝
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Sorry, Goose.{\r}

346
00:26:55,850 --> 00:27:00,913
我們見過米格28連續做四個負重力俯衝
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}We happened to see a MiG-28 do a four-G negative dive.{\r}

347
00:27:01,122 --> 00:27:03,818
