349
00:27:07,095 --> 00:27:08,824
是機密資料
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}It's classified.{\r}

350
00:27:09,030 --> 00:27:10,588
我可以告訴你 但是之後就要殺了你
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}I could tell you, but I'd have to kill you.{\r}

351
00:27:10,798 --> 00:27:13,824
上尉，我有權知道最高機密
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Lieutenant, I have top-secret clearance.{\r}

352
00:27:14,035 --> 00:27:16,833
五角大樓允許我比你知道得更多
