{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}- It was a nice picture. - Lieutenant.{\r}

368
00:28:07,088 --> 00:28:08,988
你當時在做什麼？
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}What were you doing there?{\r}

369
00:28:09,757 --> 00:28:12,521
- 溝通 - 是溝通
