373
00:28:22,236 --> 00:28:24,830
對不起，我討厭它這樣
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}I'm sorry, I hate it when it does that. I'm sorry.{\r}

374
00:28:25,873 --> 00:28:27,738
對不起
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Excuse me.{\r}

375
00:28:27,942 --> 00:28:29,671
原來是你
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}So you're the one.{\r}

376
00:28:30,478 --> 00:28:32,537
