378
00:28:35,650 --> 00:28:39,546
這次飛行的規定高度在一萬英尺 無論如何不能低於這個高度
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}The hard deck on this hop will be 10000 feet. There'll be no engagement below that.{\r}

379
00:28:40,221 --> 00:28:42,348
出發
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Move it.{\r}

380
00:28:46,527 --> 00:28:48,188
上尉
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Lieutenant.{\r}

381
00:28:49,931 --> 00:28:52,331
