{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}I see 20 new hotshots every eight weeks.{\r}

389
00:29:09,751 --> 00:29:12,151
你一定能想像得到
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Now, I'm sure you can figure that out.{\r}

390
00:29:12,353 --> 00:29:14,446
上尉
