409
00:30:35,736 --> 00:30:38,398
來吧，傑斯特 看看我能不能逼你使出全力
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Come on, Jester. Let's see if I can give you a run for your money here.{\r}

410
00:30:44,879 --> 00:30:46,847
小心撞到山
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}Watch the mountains.{\r}

411
00:30:56,958 --> 00:30:58,823
他仍然在後面
{\fscx75\fscy75\1c&H80FFFF&\3c&HFF0000&}I still got him. He's still back there.{\r}

412
00:30:59,026 --> 00:31:01,085
